# Privacy Policy

This policy applies to all information collected or submitted on Scorekeeper Lite's app for iPhone and any other devices and platforms.

## Information we collect

No account is needed to utilize Scorekeeper Lite. No information is stored from the user onto our app aside from user defaults for the app memory. Scorekeeper Lite will not ask you for your name, address, email address, or phone number. 

## Technical basics

Scorekeeper Lite currently does not use any notifications. 
Scorekeeper Lite currently does not allow the user to upload any files.
No passwords, fingerprint authentication, or face identification is used for Scorekeeper Lite.

## Ads and analytics
Scorekeeper Lite does not currently support ads so no data is collected from the user to personalize ad experience. 

## Information usage
Scorekeeper Lite does not collect any information to help operate and improve it's performance.

## Third-party links and content
Scorekeeper Lite does not use any third-party companies for its performance.

## Your Consent
By using our site or apps, you consent to our privacy policy.

## Contacting Us
If you have questions regarding this privacy policy, you may email thomas.r.kellough@gmail.com.

## Changes to this policy
If we decide to change our privacy policy, we will post those changes on this page.
